                                <span >Why</span>
                                    <span  class="accent cornflower-text">W&L</span>
                            </p>
                                <div class="body-copy">
                                    <p >Washington and Lee University is a small liberal arts college nestled in the Virginia mountains. We are known for our personal and engaging undergraduate experience and highly regarded School of Law.</p>
                                </div>
                        </div>

