                    </p>
                                                                <p class="h3 black-text" >W&L Advantage</p>
                                            <div class="slate-text">
                            <p >Founded in 1749, W&L is the 9th oldest college in the United States, even older than the U.S. Constitution.<br /><br />
Today, W&L is a top-ranked liberal arts university that continues to build on its innovative and flexible approach to education. W&L’s motto, “Not unmindful of the future,” reflects our commitment to an education that is relevant to the 21st century. </p>
                        </div>

                        <ul class="list-links">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/academics/areas-of-study" title="Discover Majors and Minors">Discover Majors and Minors<span class="wlu-icon"><svg><use xlink:href="Content/assets/icons/icon-defs.svg#icon-arrow-right"></use></svg></span></a>
