                            <img src="/assets/Homepage/making-college-affordable.jpg"    alt="" />
 
                    </p>
                                                                <p class="h3 black-text" >Making College Affordable</p>
                                            <div class="slate-text">
                            <p >We are committed to meeting 100% of student financial need.<br /><br />
Every year, W&L awards about $53 million in institutional grants in addition to federal and state awards. And because of the strength of our need-based aid, only a fraction of families choose to take out optional loans. </p>
                        </div>

                        <ul class="list-links">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/admissions/financial-aid" title="Discover Scholarships and Aid">Discover Scholarships and Aid<span class="wlu-icon"><svg><use xlink:href="Content/assets/icons/icon-defs.svg#icon-arrow-right"></use></svg></span></a>
                                </li>
