                    </p>
                                                                <p class="h3 black-text" >Pool of Opportunities</p>
                                            <div class="slate-text">
                            <p >Our size, resources and commitment to innovation mean students have access to faculty and resources from day one.<br /><br />
One of the hallmarks of the W&L experience is the accessibility of faculty. Every class is taught by a faculty member who often becomes a mentor, colleague and champion, pushing students to raise the bar. </p>
                        </div>

                        <ul class="list-links">
