                    </p>
                                                                <p class="h3 black-text" >Adventure-Ready Location</p>
                                            <div class="slate-text">
                            <p >Our campus is about 50 miles from Roanoke, 140 miles from the state capital of Richmond, and 180 miles from the national capital of Washington, D.C.<br /><br />
Lexington — and the adventure-ready landscape that surrounds it — become such a part of students’ lives that graduates often return to visit long after their college days are behind them.</p>
