                                                        </p>


                                                                                                        <p class="h4"><a class="black-text" href="https://columns.wlu.edu/wl-student-performs-at-havana-jazz-festival/">W&#038;L Student Performs at Havana Jazz Festival</a></p>
                                                                                                    <p>A meeting with a Broadway legend allowed engineering major Zaria Daniels ’26 to take her vocal talents to Cuba.</p>

                                                    <p>
                                                        <a class="text-cta lava-text" href="https://columns.wlu.edu/wl-student-performs-at-havana-jazz-festival/">
