                                                        </p>


                                                                                                        <p class="h4"><a class="black-text" href="https://columns.wlu.edu/exploring-careers-in-the-big-apple/">Exploring Careers in the Big Apple</a></p>
                                                                                                    <p>W&L's Office of Career and Professional Development gave students the opportunity to network and explore potential career paths over Washington Break.</p>

