                                                                                                        <p class="h4"><a class="black-text" href="https://columns.wlu.edu/alex-miller-named-next-vice-president-for-student-affairs-and-dean-of-students-at-washington-and-lee/">Alex Miller Named Next Vice President for Student Affairs and Dean of Students at Washington and Lee</a></p>
                                                                                                    <p>Miller, whose appointment is effective July 1, joined Denison as vice president of student life in 2020 and has over 20 years of experience in higher education as a student affairs professional. </p>

                                                    <p>
                                                        <a class="text-cta lava-text" href="https://columns.wlu.edu/alex-miller-named-next-vice-president-for-student-affairs-and-dean-of-students-at-washington-and-lee/">
